    Im phat tired and some mobs are up so i will be fast.<br>
Wanted to explore this zone a little more and as that we have enough keys, we did it yesterday.<br>
Motg is now a possae, he droped a Monster Summoning III scroll.
<br><br>
Then we headed to the Progenitor room, this guy is a damn freaking big golem. He hit fast and the fight was really close, he died anyways and gave us our first ever Primal weapon, grats Zzijah on the Primal Lance!

